      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — nominal completion",
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry data compared against CFD velocity fields at 5 flow-speed operating points. All simulation runs completed to nominal termination with no solver interruptions reported. Residuals converged to specified tolerances. No edge-case or off-design fault conditions were exercised."
