      "rationale": "MMS verification confirms second-order spatial accuracy for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver. Hemolysis scalar transport equation verified against analytical solutions for simple shear flow. All verification cases completed to nominal termination with residuals meeting specified convergence criteria."
