      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Discretization error estimated using GCI or equivalent Richardson extrapolation approach; error contribution to QoI within acceptable bounds for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Grid convergence index computed across three mesh refinement levels (coarse: 4.2M cells, medium: 11.7M cells, fine: 28.4M cells). GCI for the hemolysis index QoI is 3.8% on the medium mesh, accepted as within bounds for MRL 2. Temporal discretization error assessed via time-step refinement study showing less than 1.5% variation in RH."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
