      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative flow conditions. Fluid properties match clinical CPB blood analog specifications. Operating envelope spans the full range of COU flow-speed combinations. Geometric similarity between validation and COU pump confirmed through dimensional analysis."
    },
    {
