    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Validation results across 4 studies all completed nominally with quantitative agreement within defined acceptance bounds. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The assessment team notes that solver robustness was studied informally during development; this is considered adequate for MRL 2 given that all validation runs completed to nominal termination without observed numerical failures.",
